message: >-
  If you use GeoSync in academic research, industry reports, or derivative
  work, please cite it using the metadata below.
title: "GeoSync: Geometric Market Intelligence Platform"
abstract: >-
  GeoSync is a production-grade quantitative research infrastructure that
  applies differential geometry, synchronization theory, and non-equilibrium
  thermodynamics to financial market analysis. The platform implements
  Kuramoto phase synchronization, Ollivier-Ricci curvature flow, fractal
  dynamics, and free-energy-minimizing neuro-symbolic control, exposed
  through a deterministic event-driven backtester, a governance-aligned
  execution fabric, and a comprehensive observability stack.
type: software
